{"tid":232623,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"（搵漫畫）想搵一套漫畫","createTime":"2017-05-07T01:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T01:43:40.000Z","uid":89979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02d3caca8ce08093527dfe6a6185d3ae0abf6b13","tid":232623,"uid":89979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:19:57.000Z","msg":"細個個時睇過套漫畫，得9集，係d超能力打架漫畫，主角個能力係爆破，第一話一開始就係講主角拆屋，最後果集係係間工廠打大佬，個大佬好似係佢老豆。<br />\n我明明記得細個睇果時叫破壞王，但係呢排上網搵到果套破壞王完全唔係我記憶中果套，有冇人睇過可以話比我知套野叫咩名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef39847f6a3a86502207bd105e2361f2a6d0ce2d","tid":232623,"uid":89979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:43:40.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇過，童年點憶黎，搵左好耐都搵唔到，有冇人幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}